User:

write a code in c for sum of n numbers

Assistant:

Sure! Here is a simple C program that calculates the sum of a given number of integers:
```
#include <stdio.h>

int main() {
  // Declare variables
  int n, i, sum = 0;

  // Get the number of integers from the user
  printf("Enter the number of integers you want to sum: ");
  scanf("%d", &n);

  // Get the integers from the user and add them to the sum
  for (i = 1; i <= n; i++) {
    int num;
    printf("Enter integer %d: ", i);
    scanf("%d", &num);
    sum += num;
  }

  // Print the sum
  printf("The sum is: %d\n", sum);

  return 0;
}
```
This program prompts the user to enter the number of integers they want to sum, and then asks for each integer. It then calculates and prints the sum of all the integers.

I hope this helps! Let me know if you have any questions.

